{"tid":1417244,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣入] 唔係口號嘅問題 係宣傳不足令人唔知 光復香港 時代革命 點解","createTime":"2019-08-05T16:13:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T06:40:12.000Z","uid":135891,"like":42,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"9abb63e79146aa4d248943f2f046c13a700f8fcf","tid":1417244,"uid":135891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:13:52.000Z","msg":"成日話同温層 市民大眾唔知點解就要避開<br />\n記唔記得當初五六月民意民智都係靠我地一張張傳單 一幅幅文宣贏返嚟<br />\n<br />\n係文宣 令市民大眾知點解要反送中<br />\n係文宣 令市民大眾知點解變咗五大訴求<br />\n係文宣 令市民大眾知點解要入立法會<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">咁今次就用文宣令市民大眾知咩叫</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n佢地當初都唔明咩係反送中架 都唔明點解要衝擊架 唔明唔係要斬腳趾避沙蟲 而係令到佢地明<br />\n<br />\n解釋如下 絕對合法正當 不含港獨成份<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/htMSAFj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhtMSAFj.jpg&h=423c948e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\ncap圖想方便大家睇 請順手支持下佢地個 page<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B0nhE5uJXPy/?igshid=t2hd28b0hoc1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB0nhE5uJXPy%2F%3Figshid%3Dt2hd28b0hoc1&d=aRHHWgZm4a4JNL46Iov0BC9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=1cd2904b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB0nhE5uJXPy%2F%3Figshid%3Dt2hd28b0hoc1&h=912e6605\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B0nhE5uJXPy/?igshid=t2hd28b0hoc1</a>"},{"pid":"e51702923fb5e68a8a9e23312a99b850a0849b8d","tid":1417244,"uid":261914,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:15:02.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"901bdc5adad21f15cbb81f874d5a663cb1f0d4b2","tid":1417244,"uid":135891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:15:24.000Z","msg":"唔好斬腳趾避沙蟲"},{"pid":"e8ee40b30afa989cef178ba53910d1f23031ac5d","tid":1417244,"uid":135891,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:16:34.000Z","msg":"我地